{"type":"message","id":"ba57d729","parentId":"ec422d3a","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:49:20.189Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-28 23:49 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下4个主题的**最新**行业动态（2026年3月），每个主题找到3-5条最新信息，整理成结构化内容：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：最新政策、市场动态、典型案例\n2. **智能安防/视频监控**：最新技术、市场趋势、厂商动态\n3. **IT运维服务/AIOps**：最新产品发布、技术突破、市场变化\n4. **网络系统集成/综合布线**：最新项目动态、技术标准\n\n要求：\n- 优先搜索2026年3月内的新闻\n- 每条信息包含：时间、标题、核心内容（2-3句话）\n- 整理成可直接追加到学习笔记的Markdown格式\n- 输出语言：中文\n\n完成后返回整理好的Markdown内容。"}],"timestamp":1774712960186}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e979969","parentId":"ba57d729","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:49:24.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to search for the latest industry news (March 2026) for 4 topics:\n1. Enterprise Digital Transformation\n2. Smart Security/Video Surveillance\n3. IT Operations Services/AIOps\n4. Network System Integration/Cabling\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"497ec1a0535aaf20a8dc35d64593f6b39582a040eaa85db318310b938e96b688"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_51yadkvj68qf_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":103,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42228,"totalTokens":42448,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001236,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00506736,"total":0.00522606}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774712960187}}
{"type":"message","id":"48491063","parentId":"2e979969","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:49:24.969Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_51yadkvj68qf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774712964966}}
